ZTSD_IPI-WERKS .
ZVSD_IPI-TXJCD =
ZTSD_IPI-TXJCD .
ZVSD_IPI-BRSCH =
ZTSD_IPI-BRSCH .
ZVSD_IPI-MATKL =
ZTSD_IPI-MATKL .
ZVSD_IPI-TAXLAW =
ZTSD_IPI-TAXLAW .
<VIM_TOTAL_STRUC> = ZVSD_IPI.
    APPEND TOTAL.
  ENDSELECT.
  SORT TOTAL BY <VIM_XTOTAL_KEY>.
  <STATUS>-ALR_SORTED = 'R'.
*.check dynamic selectoptions (not in DDIC)...........................*
  IF X_HEADER-SELECTION NE SPACE.
    PERFORM CHECK_DYNAMIC_SELECT_OPTIONS.
  ELSEIF X_HEADER-DELMDTFLAG NE SPACE.
    PERFORM BUILD_MAINKEY_TAB.
  ENDIF.
  REFRESH EXTRACT.
ENDFORM.
